Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是美國公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"We are citizens of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們被作為人質扣押\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have been taken hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會和罪犯弗蘭克·安德伍德溝通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will not communicate with the criminal Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只和他的繼任者威廉·康威溝通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will only communicate with his successor, William Conway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么滿足我們的要求  否則他們就得死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either you give us what we want or we kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他偷了你的總統之位你就不生氣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aren't you angry that he stole your presidency?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃克公開聲明了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Walker went on record.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們站出來  他就完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I go on the record, he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉錄  馬上做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Transcribe this, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要在文章里寫我們曾威脅曝光他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's putting in the article that we threatened to expose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么會發生這種事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要成為下一位美國第一夫人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna be the next First Lady of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們讓這件事為我們所用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We make it work for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐懼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐懼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受夠了試圖贏取人心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm done trying to win over people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德或許是個壞蛋  但他不會殺人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Underwood may be a crook, but he's not a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是假定他會死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It presumes he's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是會死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不向恐怖低頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't submit to terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們制造恐怖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We make the terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想跟你談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been meaning to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕  不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's terrifying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統和我有一個簡單的請求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president and I have a simple request.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我們你看到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你周圍有任何東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If anything in your environment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你覺得奇怪  不對勁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}strikes you as a bit odd, a bit off,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿起電話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}pick up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是個包裹  還是不太對勁的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whether it's a package or a person that seems out of place,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們希望你通知我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'd love you to let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如今外面有很多雜音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because there's a lot of noise out there these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媒體嘰嘰喳喳  沉湎于過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A noisy press that's choosing to dwell on the past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不關注當下的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}instead of what's happening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫和我想保護你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My husband and I want to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩周后  你們將前往投票箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In two weeks' time, you will be heading to the ballot box
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定你們要生活在怎樣的國家里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to decide what kind of country you want to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個選擇影響深遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a profound choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不管誰贏得選舉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But no matter who wins this election,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得通力合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we're going to need to work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相照應\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watch out for each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  也互相監督\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, yes, watch each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以確保所有人的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to keep us all safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我們你看到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫克萊爾·安德伍德  我認可這則信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is Claire Underwood, and I approve this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要再拍一條嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we do one more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民主黨來了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did the Democrats show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒讓人失望  幾乎都來了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They didn't disappoint. Almost every member, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-幾乎  -我列了到場名單\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Almost. - I have a list of those who did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位國會議員  我不需要《華盛頓先驅報》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My fellow congressmen, I do not need the Washington Herald
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我白宮里住了個惡棍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to tell me that a scoundrel lives in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到民主黨來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see the Democrats are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們急著辯論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're eager to debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對過道另一邊的先生們說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say to the gentlemen on the other side of the aisle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是否該調查總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we investigate the president
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在就任副總統期間犯下的罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for crimes committed while he was vice president?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  好  我們辯論吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say, yes. Let's debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們整日整夜地辯論這惡棍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's debate this miscreant all day and all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長女士  議事詢問\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Speaker. Parliamentary inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐治亞州的議員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The gentleman from Georgia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請提出他的議事詢問\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}may state the nature of his parliamentary inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道按眾議院規則\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do the rules of the House not require
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統不是該受到正式邀請才能出席嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the president be formally invited in order to attend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長女士  容我說一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Speaker, if I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長有請南卡羅萊納州議員說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Speaker recognizes the gentleman from South Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統今天戴了他的國會胸針\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president is wearing his congressional pin today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他可以出席一切會議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and is thereby welcome to any and all proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長女士  議長女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Speaker! Madam Speaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按眾議院規則\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rules of the House state
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前眾議院成員若與議題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that former members are not allowed on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有直接關系則不得參與辯論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they have interest in the matter under debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Speaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統對今天的議題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the president has no interest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既無關聯  也無意見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or opinion on the matter being debated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾議院安靜  眾議院安靜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The House suspend. The House will suspend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長女士  我還在講話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Speaker, I still do have the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我難以相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I find it hard to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統對議題無話可說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the president wouldn't have an opinion on the matter being discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果佛羅里達州議員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the good gentleman from Florida
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯讓出點時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would yield a portion of his time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的疑問肯定能得到解答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assure him it will satisfy his query.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給黨領袖三分鐘時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I yield three minutes to the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我的時間讓給前南卡羅萊納州議員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I yield my time to the former congressman from South Carolina
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現美國總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議事程序  議事詢問\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Point of order! Parliamentary inquiry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議事詢問\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Parliamentary inquiry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議事詢問\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Parliamentary inquiry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  這太不尋常了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President. This is beyond the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I also do not care
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的調查委員會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about your investigative committees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那不是我今天關心的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that is not what I care about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾議院安靜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The House will cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我今天關心的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is not what I care about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去出席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am on my way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個美國愛國者的葬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the funeral of an American patriot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個好人  一個丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A good man, a husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美國境內被人砍頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who was beheaded on American soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾議院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻在今天辯論我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}chooses to debate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-眾議院安靜  -我要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The House will suspend. - I asked to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向眾議院發表講話  卻遭到拒絕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to a full session of this chamber and my requests were denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-議長女士  -總統先生  你必須讓出說話權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Madam Speaker! - Mr. President, you must yield the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會退讓的  議長女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not yield, Madam Speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我等不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一個殺人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the murderers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺害了吉姆·米勒先生的一個殺人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the murderers who killed Mr. Jim Miller...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還逍遙法外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在逃逸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At large.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還要多少證據\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much more proof do you people need?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求所有眾議院議員表明立場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I demand that every member of this House take a stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像曾經的羅斯福  再之前的威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like FDR before, and Wilson before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求國會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I demand that this Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式對哈里發國宣戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}declare a formal declaration of war against ICO,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在本土  也在海外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}both here and abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動議休會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Motion to adjourn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-支持  -眾議院休會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Second! - The House will adjourn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統請停止講話  -我不會停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The president will cease. - I will not cease!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will never cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求國會宣布美利堅合眾國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I demand that this Congress declare a state of war
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經并且正在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has existed and does exist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與哈里發國交戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}between ICO and the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求所有眾議院成員留在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I demand that every member of this House stay in this chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for as long as it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你們對我的要求作出表決\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you bring my request to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則你們將被歷史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you will all go down in history
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銘記為懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請警衛官帶走總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sergeant at arms will remove the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長女士  我重復  我要求投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Speaker, I repeat. I demand a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會退讓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會退讓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會退讓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據稱的恐怖分子扎克瑞·霍松被聯調局擊斃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alleged terrorist Zachary Hawthorne was killed by the FBI,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但約書亞·馬斯特森仍在逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but Joshua Masterson is still at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米勒一家哀悼之時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}While the Miller family mourns,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對逃跑的恐怖分子的搜尋仍在繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the hunt for the missing terrorist continues
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣氛十分緊張\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and tensions are running high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統雖然提出戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president may be asking for war,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看來他已經遭遇了戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it seems war's already been declared on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的粉絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局正在調查查塔努加市的一起連環槍擊案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}FBI is looking into a multiple shooting in Chattanooga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-據報稱是與黑幫有關  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Reports have it gang related. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西弗吉尼亞州一架私人飛機墜毀  機械故障\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A private plane went down in West Virginia. Mechanical failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐治亞州多處房屋失火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A series of homes were set on fire in Georgia,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能是縱火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}most likely arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北卡羅來納州一家便利店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Convenience store in North Carolina
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晨4點左右爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}exploded at about 4:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-商店在哪  -羅利郊外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's the store? - Uh, suburb outside of Raleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起因仍在調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cause is still under investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我去露個臉  -是  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll make an appearance. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加在日程里  讓媒體有時間出動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just put it on the schedule so the media has time to mobilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統對約書亞·馬斯特森宣戰了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I take it the president has declared war on Joshua Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就不該不讓我繼續參加通話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He never should've kicked me off that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天早晨的重點不是政治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this morning isn't about politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得對生者表示同情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to show some compassion for the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對死者表示尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And respect for the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一家答應了短暫見面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The family's agreed to a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有媒體  不做講話  但我們應該能做點什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No press, no speeches, but we should be able to pull something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統先生  -州長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. President. - Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不知道我們已經為他們做了什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do they not realize what we've done for them already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我說了  先生  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I pointed that out, sir, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們家的女兒服了藥  目前很脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the daughter's medicated and very fragile at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米勒太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我非常遺憾  -謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm so very sorry. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I promise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不會罷休\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not stop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非所有導致了這場慘劇的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until everyone responsible for this terrible tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都受到裁決\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓  上帝為證\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I swear to you, as God is my witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不會有人傷害你和你的家人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no one will ever harm you or your family ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉國與你和你女兒同哀  米勒太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The nation mourns with you and your daughter, Mrs. Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-謝謝  如果你不介意  -當然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. If you don't mind... - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be right along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天很忙  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a busy day for you today, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很悲傷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a sad, sad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾結果是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a shame things didn't turn out differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  有些事比我們倆重要  威爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Well, some things are bigger than the two of us, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望他在場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜  梅莉莎  求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Calm down, Melissa. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪他  他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's his fault. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸死了  他殺了他  -求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Daddy's dead. He killed him. - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我點時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你吃藥了嗎  -吃了  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did you take your medicine? - Yes. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了  吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天這樣的日子  你會去想  該說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do. You think about what you would say on a day like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果今天這樣的日子出現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If a day like today were to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你會讓它過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you let it pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你知道  你未來還有漫長的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you know you have so much more left ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多事可以一起做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So much to do together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會想  你想40分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think... You think 40 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們遲了40分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we were late 40 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是兩分鐘  哪怕一分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or two, or one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是我們當時去了別處吃飯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or if we went somewhere else to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沉湎過去  活在假設里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to dwell in the past, to live in what-ifs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我丈夫的為人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-親愛的  -求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Honey... - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想說說我父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to say about my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那么堅強  那么勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was so strong... so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親本打算帶我們去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father was taking us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒事  寶貝  沒事的  -我父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on, baby. It's okay. - My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺了我父親  他是因為你才死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You killed my father. You're the reason he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Melissa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  梅莉莎  我們理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right, Melissa. We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你死  而她當上總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you die and she becomes president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩對你說了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did the girl say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說她希望我死  而你當上總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said she hopes I die and that you become the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麥卡倫先生  我是國安局副局長邁克爾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Macallan, this is Deputy Director Michaels from the NSA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在你辦公室  我們安排了會面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm literally in your office. I believe we had a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從北到南已經展開了大范圍搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's been raids as far up as New York and down to the panhandle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前為止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As of now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格林主要在搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Green's focusing in on the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗吉尼亞和北卡羅來納的交界處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}border between Virginia and North Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽斯為今天下午的事準備好了聲明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth has a statement ready for this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  最好的聲明就是不做聲明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. The best statement is no statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說  我們準備好前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, I want Claire to be the voice on this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要克萊爾來就此事發聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-外面人好多  -我們最好先讓博奇進來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Quite a crowd out there. - Well, we better bring Birch in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博奇議員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鮑勃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早的事能載入史冊了  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that was a little bit of history this morning, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可不是呢  -我看不出有別的辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It certainly was. - I couldn't see it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No disagreement from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解共和黨的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you know how the Republicans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優柔寡斷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything but a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們錯把抱怨當做了領導\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They mistake complaint for leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒有調查你的委員會了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, instead of a committee to investigate you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是成立了討論宣戰的委員會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you got one to discuss your declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到選舉日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the way to election day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕有那么一小撮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if there's only a handful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勇氣和決心敢抵抗的共和黨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Republicans with the grit and spit to put up a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都能控制輿論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can control the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們談什么都好  就是別談那篇文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get them talking about anything but that goddamn article.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我們這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Now, who from our side
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-得去安撫誰  -烏麥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- do we need to massage? - Womack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那聲明讓他措手不及  得讓他別摻和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The declaration caught him off guard. Had to keep him out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他的選民真要去打仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's his constituents that actually fight the damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請尊敬的密蘇里州議員進來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's call in the honorable gentleman from Missouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他喜歡波本吧  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, he's a bourbon man, isn't he? - Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噱頭  是的  我說這是噱頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A stunt. Yes, I'm calling it a stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  容我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie, if I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆  請說說  你什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, please, what are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這宣戰請求不過又是在分散注意力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This request for a declaration of war is yet another distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從未像今天這樣為總統自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I've never been prouder of the president than I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在否認米勒一家的遭遇  那是個慘劇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not denying what happened to the Millers. It was a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你在否認  否認它就是慘劇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but you are. Because denying it is the tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個規律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫的政府  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your husband's administration, Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-繼續在暗箱操作  -湯姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- continues to operate in the shadows. - Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你相信你的文章很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand you believe in the importance of your article.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應今天來跟你談談它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I agreed to come here today and talk with you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們正在奮力保護國家的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're fighting to keep this country safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮尚未發表任何關于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the White House has yet to release one piece of information
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓捕那些國內恐怖分子的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about the attempted capture of those domestic terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里發國恐怖分子  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ICO terrorists, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據幾小時前的報告稱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reports from a few hours ago
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在北卡羅來納或弗吉尼亞州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are saying North Carolina or Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但目前也只有這些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's all we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在慢慢收緊包圍圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we are circling in, we're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的情報部門  是真正的英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our intelligence community, they are the real heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  請回到我的點上  我的消息源確認\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie, if we could get back to my point, my sources confirmed--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海瑟·鄧巴  她不是我或我丈夫的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heather Dunbar, no friend of mine or my husband's,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查過這些指控  但宣布總統無罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}looked into these charges, and cleared the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無罪  得了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleared? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮自《先驅報》刊登了我的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The White House has not had a single press briefing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒舉行過一次新聞發布會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since the Herald ran my article.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總說白宮不就此事發言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You keep saying the White House isn't speaking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我正坐在這里跟你說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sitting right here talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是雷米·丹頓或杰姬·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not Remy Danton or Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or Lucas Goodwin, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -什么意思  盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - Excuse me. Lucas Goodwin, meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說  我  我在這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm saying, me. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道這些話我們還要說多少遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I don't know how many more times we have to go over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆·漢默施密特的文章以前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, a Tom Hammerschmidt article used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我打開《華盛頓先驅報》后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the first thing I would look for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個要找的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I opened the Washington Herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫婦停止了競選宣傳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Underwoods are no longer campaigning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們想怎么說怎么說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can call it what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想想過去的幾天  想想現在的氣氛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if you think about the last few days, what's in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我們慢慢來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might not be such a bad idea for us to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是壞事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}take it one handshake at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者實話實說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or call it for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"國內和國外"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Home and abroad."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統基本上在要求許可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president is essentially asking for permission
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們的國土上打仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to fight a war on our soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能太強烈反對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't push back too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能顯得好像對恐怖主義手軟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't afford to look soft on terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不能視而不見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't look the other way, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最清楚這樣的話會帶來的結果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You of all people know where this kind of talk leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里發國和美利堅合眾國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...ICO and the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確保處理宣戰的委員會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make sure the committee dealing with the declaration of war
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會進入表決\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}never gets to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不反對戰爭  我們反對他的戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not against war, we're against his.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你聯絡議長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want you to reach out to the Speaker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查明她要安排誰進入那個委員會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and find out who she's putting on that committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得回到總統罪行的問題上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to get back to the president's crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是新聞  唯一的新聞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the story. It's the only story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有別的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有我的稿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have my script.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會退讓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not yield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道他說了什么  什么時候說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know what he says and when he says it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍可不習慣接受命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our general isn't used to taking orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾  還有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -你妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - Your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我們在波利跳上展開了宣傳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I know we opened up this campaign on Pollyhop,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但或許該中止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it might be time to close it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或至少也該小心點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or at least be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們查到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what did they find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在找的那名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The home of the mother of the terrorist,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子的母親家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, the one they're looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚遭人破壞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was vandalized last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車庫被燒  窗戶被打破\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garage set on fire. Broken windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, uh, Hannah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她發了視頻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well... she posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在網上維護了那位母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was defending the mother online.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么時候  -今天下午\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When? - This afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時機可不妙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The timing is not good on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我給你看  -等會兒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can show you. - Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康威州長和我很榮幸能來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Governor Conway and I are honored to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪伴米勒一家和他們的親友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the Miller family and their closest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道海外退伍軍人協會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know the VFW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吉姆在諾克斯維爾生活的重要部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was a big part of Jim's life here in Knoxville.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在國土安全部和我們熱線的幫助下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the help of Homeland and our hotline,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們認為馬斯特森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we think that Masterson
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經進入了弗吉尼亞州的西南角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has crossed into the southwest corner of Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在斯考特或華盛頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scott or Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-然后呢  -然后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And? - And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格林助理局長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assistant Director Green?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在依靠空中支援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're relying on aerial support,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目擊和當地執法部門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sightings and local law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們比較確信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're fairly confident
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以在接下來24小時內找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can have him pinned down in the next 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統要我們完全確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president wants us to be absolutely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能允許他再跑掉了  這事關飯碗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't have him getting away again. Careers are at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這桌上的每個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone around this table
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都清楚情況的嚴重性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is fully aware of the gravity of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  總統知道了會很高興的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. The president will be happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你想要什么樣的吻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. What kind of kiss do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-愛斯基摩  -快進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Eskimo. - In...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你生氣了  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're angry. - I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被提了問  我回答了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was asked a question and I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得太輕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the least of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我現在不想談這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, well, I don't want to talk about it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想輸掉競選嗎  是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you trying to lose this election? Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾  得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你維護的這女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This woman that you're defending...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她兒子砍了別人的頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her son just cut someone's head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還逍遙在外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's still out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知道這看上去什么樣嗎  -別說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you understand what this looks like? - Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我們兒子為什么睡不著嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want to know why our son can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才八歲  卻失眠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's eight years old, and he can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他做惡夢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he's having nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他覺得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒店里有頭黑色大狗在到處跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a big black dog running around the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-狗  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Dog? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他閉上眼睛  就能聽到它咆哮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He closes his eyes, and he can hear it growling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他害怕  威爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's scared, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說那些話是因為那女人也是受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said what I said because that woman is a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這必須停止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it has to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去給自己倒一杯酒  我就回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get yourself a drink. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他母親  這是漢娜的回應\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the mother. And this is Hannah's response.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not a criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不該因為她兒子的罪受懲罰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and should not be punished for the sins of her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我們都反對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all, I know, reject
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.61,0:23:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩位困惑受傷的青年的說法和行為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the rhetoric and actions of these damaged, troubled young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說  這是該反省的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I mean is, this is a time for reflection,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是進攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not aggression...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她沒有表示寬恕  但表示了同情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So she's not condoning it, but it is sympathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把約書亞和扎克瑞說成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plays into the idea that Joshua and Zachary
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一對兒尋找目標的困惑青年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were just a pair of troubled kids looking for a cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:23:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟普通學校槍擊手沒什么區別\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no different than some school shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視頻轉發超過10萬次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The post has been shared over 100,000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟她談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to talk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-漢娜  -那個母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hannah? - The mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直對你在哪露面十分小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been very careful about where you appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,0:24:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-莉安  能讓我們單獨待會兒嗎  -當然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- LeAnn, will you excuse us for a moment? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得加大恐懼感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to dial up the terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個母親能幫我們做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the mother can help us with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.36,0:24:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那樣我們還得找到馬斯特森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that also means we have to locate Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.01,0:24:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆在等我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.32,0:24:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.66,0:24:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.63,0:24:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不該在葬禮上哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't have cried at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.02,0:24:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  那效果很好  -對我不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, it played beautifully. - Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.25,0:25:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.28,0:25:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  告訴他你要遲點到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Just tell him you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.61,0:25:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統先生  -沒事  警官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. President. - It's all right, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.51,0:25:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.81,0:25:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能給我你的目鏡嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I have your scope?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.81,0:25:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你槍上的目鏡  我保證還回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scope on your gun. I promise I'll give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.39,0:25:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.07,0:25:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你把目鏡舉在離臉稍遠處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if you just hold the scope a little a ways from your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.13,0:25:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往下看  直向下  草坪對面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and look down, straight down, across the lawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.61,0:25:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.00,0:26:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他們了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.58,0:26:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人想要發聲  有些是支持的  有些反對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those people want a voice. Some for, some against.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.80,0:26:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們也在草坪那頭往這邊看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're looking back across the lawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.56,0:26:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這棟房子  這些窗戶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}toward this house and these windows...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.72,0:26:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.72,0:26:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"不知道總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I wonder what the president
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.26,0:26:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和第一夫人今晚在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the First Lady are doing tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們能保護我們嗎"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And will they be able to protect us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.03,0:26:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該在場的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.53,0:26:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.28,0:26:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受槍傷時  我真該在場的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you got shot. I wish I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.74,0:26:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我還能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I could've...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.51,0:26:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}protected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.78,0:26:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧  那些人只想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, all those people want...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.82,0:26:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人保護他們  不用面對可怕的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is someone to keep them from what they're afraid to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:26:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統和第一夫人今晚要做什么呢  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what are the president and First Lady doing tonight, Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.08,0:27:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托馬斯不是還等著你呢嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I believe Thomas is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.30,0:27:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.93,0:27:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明早見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.99,0:27:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有煙嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.41,0:27:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.42,0:27:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我知道我的人民今晚在想什么*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*I know what my people are thinking tonight*
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.42,0:27:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17\bord0\shad0\an9\fad(1000,1000)\fn微软雅黑}BGM: I Wonder What the King Is Doing Tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.32,0:27:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*穿過陰影  他們漫步回家*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*As home through the shadows they wander*
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.53,0:27:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*大家都竊笑著*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Everyone smiling in secret delight*
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.75,0:27:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*他們看著城堡  思索著*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*As they stare at the castle and ponder*
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.95,0:27:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*當風往這邊吹*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*And whenever the wind blows this way*
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.58,0:27:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*你幾乎能聽到大家說*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*You can almost hear everyone say*
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.47,0:27:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*不知國王今晚在做什么*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*I wonder what the king is doing tonight*
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.47,0:28:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.38,0:28:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我餓了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.50,0:28:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以去了主廚房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I went down to the main kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.77,0:28:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面的人真不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a lovely group of people you have down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.93,0:28:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你需要什么  可以叫人拿上來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there's anything you need, it can be brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.73,0:28:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我直到吃在嘴里才知道自己需要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know what I needed until I was eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.15,0:28:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到了總統的聲明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard the president's declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.36,0:28:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.89,0:28:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟怎么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you really think?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.87,0:28:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像真的一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was almost like the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.91,0:28:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國安局的人很厲害  非常厲害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The NSA has good people. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.71,0:29:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-太厲害了  -不如你厲害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Too good. - Not as good as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.05,0:29:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足以找到我的算法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good enough to find my algorithms.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.84,0:29:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不代表他們知道我們用它做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That doesn't mean they knew what we were using them for.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.03,0:29:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.68,0:29:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前一秒  他們還叫我回家  然后緊接著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One second, they send me home, and then the next,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.06,0:29:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說  "回來"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they tell me, "Come back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.82,0:29:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們肯定要監視我了  這是個陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll been watching me. This is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.27,0:29:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是唯一的出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the only way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.11,0:29:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.26,0:29:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想要出路嗎  -你不想嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You want out? - Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}LeAnn...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.52,0:29:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們做了違法的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have done some illegal things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.10,0:29:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他競選\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are other campaigns.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.62,0:29:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-如果你可以打入國安局  -那不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If you can get into the NSA... - That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.64,0:29:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入他們的系統  你可以解決的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...into their system, you can fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你沒聽我說  -我聽了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're not listening to me. - I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.22,0:29:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解安德伍德夫婦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know the Underwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.02,0:29:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們如果想平安度過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only way that we are gonna survive this...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.35,0:29:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得讓他們贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is if they win.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.60,0:29:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以幫他們贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can help them win.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.43,0:29:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.85,0:30:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走后我就加入了報社\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got on the paper right around the time you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.73,0:30:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從時尚版塊起步的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you start in Style?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.66,0:30:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Metro desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.98,0:30:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我發了篇報道  一個街頭時尚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then I did this piece, a street fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.18,0:30:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街頭的孩子的報道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}kids on the street thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.01,0:30:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你會叫我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised you asked for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.59,0:30:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊伍里有些人員變化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people are being moved around and off the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬斯特森的報道  "戰爭  有什么好處"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Masterson story. "War, what is it good for?"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.01,0:30:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對調查性新聞感興趣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were you ever interested in investigative journalism?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.17,0:30:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要問我  不是這種的就不叫新聞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you ask me, if it's not investigating, it's not journalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽這里的人說  你能讓任何人對你開口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Word around here is you can get anybody to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.43,0:30:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過了8點  又有酒的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After 8:00, with a drink in their hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.26,0:30:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.41,0:31:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說她是個...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's the one they say you called a...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.57,0:31:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我有點緊張\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.77,0:31:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你算是傳奇人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sort of a legend and...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.60,0:31:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報道總統的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}articles on the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.98,0:31:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟你合作是莫大的榮幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'd be an honor to work with you in any capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.67,0:31:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能參與進來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.18,0:31:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們找到他了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you find him? Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.17,0:31:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等一下就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll only be another moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.37,0:31:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我已經做盡了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I've done all I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.62,0:31:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們叫我做的一切  你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything you told me to. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.21,0:31:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們知道的  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They know that, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.04,0:31:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.24,0:31:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟馬斯特森女士說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hoping to speak to Ms. Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.44,0:31:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我們倆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.88,0:32:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么問題嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.98,0:32:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有點極端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a bit extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.96,0:32:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把禁飛令擴大到這樣的范圍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Expanding the no-fly list to this extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.98,0:32:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單是對簽證的限制就前所未有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The restrictions on visas alone is unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.94,0:32:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要如何解釋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do we justify?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.14,0:32:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮顧問已經討論過了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The White House counsel's been all through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.68,0:32:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都白紙黑字寫著了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's there in black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.46,0:32:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們基本上是在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're virtually closing down our borders
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.65,0:32:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒有證據的情況下關閉國境  -會有的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- without any hard evidence to back it up. - It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.85,0:32:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多無辜的人正想進入這個國家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of innocent people are trying to get into this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.93,0:32:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可能因此受傷害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They could be hurt by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.62,0:32:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此大的政策變動  我想好好做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A change in policy this big, I want it done right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.77,0:32:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你讓世界知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to let the world know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.97,0:32:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們還想繼續進入這個國家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that if they want to continue coming to this country
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.22,0:32:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上我們的醫院  我們的學校  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for our hospitals, our colleges,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.86,0:32:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的高爾夫球場什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our golf courses and God knows what else...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.39,0:32:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們光是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're going to have to deliver
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.55,0:33:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的腦袋貼在棍子上燒是不夠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}more than my head on the end of a burning stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.64,0:33:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  凱茜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now look, Cathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.18,0:33:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你有辛苦經營的人脈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you have well-earned relationships out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.14,0:33:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是老交情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long-standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.26,0:33:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有保留  弗蘭西斯  我都聯絡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not holding back, Francis. I have reached out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.94,0:33:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我需要你再加把勁  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I need you to reach further.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.56,0:33:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要可行的情報\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want actionable intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.07,0:33:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要知道哈里發國在哪  或者至少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know where ICO is, or at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.48,0:33:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都在找他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that everyone's out there looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.79,0:33:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.47,0:33:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.29,0:33:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  凱茜  我知道你不會讓我失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Cathy. I know you won't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.71,0:33:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是來告訴我這個的嗎  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.85,0:33:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還在找他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still looking for him--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.05,0:33:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如果他死了  我要見到他  摸到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because if he's dead, I want to see him. To touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.41,0:33:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我是想幫忙  -馬斯特森太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm trying to help... - Ms. Masterson,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.74,0:33:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但他沒有聯系我  -求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- ...but he hasn't contacted me. - please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.39,0:33:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望他聯系我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.32,0:33:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  冷靜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.34,0:33:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不像他們說的那樣  是個禽獸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not a monster like they all say.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.34,0:34:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知何時失去了他  但他不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lost him somewhere. But he's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.43,0:34:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這世上還是有禽獸的  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But still, monsters do exist, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.02,0:34:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要律師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.37,0:34:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.04,0:34:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我不知道我為什么那么說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, I don't know why I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.01,0:34:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不知道我都在說什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why I say anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.89,0:34:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.16,0:34:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想問你一個簡單的問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to ask you a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.55,0:34:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道你家里發生的事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't you know what was going on in your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.35,0:34:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Excuse me? - You knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.87,0:34:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早在他去巴基斯坦之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even before he went to Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.98,0:34:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是你養大了他  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I mean, you raised him. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.95,0:34:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他是有問題  他迷失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. He had some problems. He got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.56,0:34:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不  不是這樣的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But no, nothing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.86,0:34:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你看到他做了什么吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you saw what he did, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.49,0:35:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -你想看嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - Would you like to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.48,0:35:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想  我們可以給你看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can show it to you, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.96,0:35:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  別\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.63,0:35:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他對那家人  對那個人做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What he did to that family, to that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.97,0:35:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么樣的人能做出這種事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What sort of person would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.76,0:35:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.53,0:35:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.37,0:35:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  很可怕  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. It's awful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.01,0:35:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.69,0:35:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天離開時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you leave today,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.05,0:35:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有記者  有攝像機在外面等著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there will be some reporters, some cameramen out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.41,0:35:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不需要說太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you don't need to say very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.45,0:35:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只需要叫約書自首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just need to ask Josh to turn himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.51,0:36:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世上還有很多辛辛苦苦的父親和母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are so many hardworking mothers and fathers out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.01,0:36:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可能發生在他們任何人身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This could've happened to any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.12,0:36:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就要抓到你兒子了  馬斯特森太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are close to capturing your son, Ms. Masterson,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.51,0:36:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會盡全力讓你見到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I will do my best to have you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.59,0:36:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.88,0:36:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人不讓你走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one's keeping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.72,0:36:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她安排了誰  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But who did she put in?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.03,0:36:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,議長安排了誰進委員會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who did the Speaker put on the committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.35,0:36:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多是席位無憂的長期議員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mostly lifers, with secure seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.22,0:36:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩兩周  很難反對戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're two weeks out. It's hard to say no to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.20,0:36:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我有共同點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I have some things in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.01,0:36:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們都討厭總統  -不  我終歸是民主黨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We both dislike the president. - No. I'm still a Democrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.89,0:36:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是右傾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who leans to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.00,0:36:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾力克斯  你的確是有些右傾的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, you do actually lean a little to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.25,0:36:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是三軍統帥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, he's the commander in chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.35,0:36:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他完全有權力決定去哪打仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got all the authority he needs to fight them where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.45,0:36:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此時此刻  國內就有個戰場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's one here. Out there, right now, as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.29,0:36:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很支持美國執法機構的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm a big fan of American law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.19,0:37:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們很快就能找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll find him soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.80,0:37:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能讓弗蘭西斯·安德伍德讓我們國家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't just let Francis Underwood turn us into a nation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.64,0:37:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得時刻心驚膽戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's always looking over their shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.95,0:37:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能擠進那個委員會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can get yourself onto that committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.71,0:37:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得主席會讓你充分表達意見的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a feeling the Chair will give you all the time you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.13,0:37:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的司機會送你回車上  但議員先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My driver will take you back to your car. But, Congressman...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.73,0:37:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.54,0:37:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I think you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.71,0:37:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你們來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much for coming out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.57,0:37:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你們來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much for coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.42,0:37:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見到你們真好  謝謝你們來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great to see you. Thanks for coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.18,0:37:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.16,0:38:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不知道自己家里發生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have no idea what is happening in your own homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.29,0:38:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他在哪嗎  馬斯特森太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you any idea where he is, Mrs. Masterson?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.93,0:38:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約書  求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josh, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.53,0:38:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你  求你自首吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}please, please turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.14,0:38:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這得停下了  不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This has all got to stop. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在財政部干了10年  他正等著呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...this after ten years with Treasury, he was waiting for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.57,0:39:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.07,0:41:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.44,0:41:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.65,0:41:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.15,0:41:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府是否認為爆炸跟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does the administration believe that the explosion was connected
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.73,0:41:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-約書亞·馬斯特森有關  -我們尚不確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- with Joshua Masterson somehow? - We're not sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.47,0:41:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多證據支持這一可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, there is strong evidence to suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.11,0:41:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店主的確是在外國出生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The owner of the establishment was foreign-born.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.38,0:41:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟海外的哈里發國有關嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any connection to ICO overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.26,0:41:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為助理局長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think our Deputy Director
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.37,0:41:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉克更有資格回答這個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clark here is better equipped to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.63,0:41:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在調查  但現在  我們設立了熱線\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're looking into it. In the meantime, we've set up a hotline.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.51,0:41:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有任何居民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If anyone in the community
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.44,0:41:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有什么...  -如果共和黨候選人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- has any-- - And if the Republican candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.66,0:41:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和余下的共和黨人不肯承認\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the rest of his party refuse to acknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.86,0:41:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國內威脅的嚴重性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the seriousness of the threat made here at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.90,0:42:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我們會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}know that we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.67,0:42:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局正在收集言論和照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The FBI is currently gathering a list of words and images.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.17,0:42:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它們出現在了你的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they appear on your children's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.27,0:42:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或你同事的設備上  請務必\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or your coworkers' devices, please--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.66,0:42:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭婊子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}War whore!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.67,0:42:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-讓開  -上車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Move! - Car!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.23,0:42:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是油漆而已  她沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was just paint. She's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.16,0:42:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有什么  說吧  道格  不會那么糟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what else? Spit it out, Doug. It won't taste so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.77,0:42:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我知道你在這事上跟我看法不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I know you disagree with me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.82,0:42:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但格林局長和他的團隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Director Green and his team
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.14,0:42:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了抓捕地點  準備行動了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have a location for the takedown and they're ready to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.45,0:42:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們確定找對地方了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're positive it's the right location?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.29,0:42:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-非常確定  -什么時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Adamant. - When?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.16,0:42:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過幾小時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.61,0:42:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以在戰況室協調\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can coordinate out of the Situation Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.14,0:42:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我要親自見他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. I'm gonna meet him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.81,0:42:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我強烈反對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I strongly advise against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.51,0:42:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  但我要到場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Duly noted, but I'll be on-site.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.27,0:42:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.56,0:43:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們隨時會爆發恐懼  真是不可思議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's amazing how ready people are to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.63,0:43:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷史會證明他們是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History would prove them right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.46,0:43:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好這個水能洗掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're lucky this is coming off with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.23,0:43:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會更糟呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could've been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.67,0:43:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點濺到你耳朵后面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some found its way behind your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.07,0:43:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我該害怕嗎  -別耍聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Should I be afraid? - Don't be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.47,0:43:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是該害怕  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.87,0:43:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從你那兒偷了東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stole something from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.18,0:43:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.92,0:43:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么無所謂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What it is, doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.70,0:43:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想要一樣你的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted something that was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.51,0:43:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.08,0:43:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀑布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Waterfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.79,0:43:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國安局用瀑布標記0day漏洞利用工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The NSA marked their zero-day exploits as waterfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.47,0:44:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們能讓我們進入什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can they get us into?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.33,0:44:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以后門進入一些很火的社交網站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can backdoor into some very popular social media.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.87,0:44:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以把任何你能想到的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can insert anything your imagination can think of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.24,0:44:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放到那些網站上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into those sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.60,0:44:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫婦或其他人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Underwoods or otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.72,0:44:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多個消息源稱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...reports coming in from a variety of sources
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.83,0:44:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當地警方和聯調局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}stating that local police enforcement and FBI agents
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.06,0:44:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在前方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are currently on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.58,0:44:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們接到報告稱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're receiving reports that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.56,0:44:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗吉尼亞州邊境有大量警力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a great deal of police activity on the Virginia border.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.55,0:44:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們目前不能確認\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cannot confirm at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.12,0:44:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們認為  這跟對國內恐怖分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we believe this is connected to the manhunt
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.85,0:44:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約書亞·馬斯特森的搜尋有關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for domestic terrorist Joshua Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.21,0:44:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約書亞·馬斯特森可能很快將被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The capture of Joshua Masterson may be close at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.05,0:44:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局仍未就此發表評論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The FBI is still not commenting,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.15,0:44:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但請看航拍情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but if you look at this aerial view,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.11,0:44:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到全副武裝的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can see heavily-armed men
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.67,0:44:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在林間穿行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}making their way through this wooded area.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.76,0:45:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  他不在這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.65,0:45:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只審出了一些零散的國內聯絡人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we have are some loose domestic connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.08,0:45:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對海外哈里發國的變態崇拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A perverse idolization of ICO overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.63,0:45:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不肯證實有大規模的國內網絡存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He refuses to confirm any wide-ranging homegrown network.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.10,0:45:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的審訊官認為此人已無價值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our interrogators are confident the asset is no longer valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.01,0:45:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒險誘供已經不可行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And risk to reward no longer tenable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.81,0:45:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我們已經到達了臨界點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, we have reached a breaking point.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.34,0:46:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我沒有已經抓到了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you think I didn't already have him?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.11,0:46:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會任他在外面流竄嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I would have left him out there somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.50,0:46:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為你了解我呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I thought you knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.60,0:46:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.31,0:46:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約書亞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Joshua.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.44,0:47:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想活嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.66,0:47:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出我們想知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.06,0:47:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出我們想知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us what we want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.75,0:47:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是個殉道者  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're no martyr, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.61,0:47:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.68,0:47:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你不是個殉道者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're not a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.45,0:47:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人會記住你所做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one will remember what you've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.00,0:47:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是在這人間  還是在你的天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}either here on Earth or in your heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.67,0:47:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么選擇米勒一家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So why did you pick the Millers?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.94,0:47:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.03,0:47:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.05,0:47:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為那女孩嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.72,0:47:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是先看上了她嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see her first?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.43,0:48:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.00,0:48:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是她先看到了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or did she see you first?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.44,0:48:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是這樣吧  她看到了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's it, isn't it? She saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.35,0:48:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一眼就看穿了你  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She looked right through you, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.53,0:48:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要再看到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need to see this person anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.74,0:48:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-處理掉他  -先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get rid of the asset. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.09,0:48:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個禽獸  但他終歸是美國公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's an animal, but he's still an American citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.01,0:48:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在交戰  他是敵方戰斗人員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are at war. And he is an enemy combatant.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.99,0:48:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他砍下那可憐人的腦袋時  就失去了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he lost whatever rights he might have had as an American
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.14,0:48:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國人的權利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when he cut that poor man's head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.31,0:48:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以少跟我說你的驕傲或立場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So don't give me your pride or your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.78,0:48:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如果你當初能照做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because none of this would have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.15,0:48:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切都不會發生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you'd done what you were told in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.71,0:48:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會處理的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.81,0:48:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當然會  而且會自愿自覺地做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you will, and you will do so willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.36,0:49:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你拍到殺他時好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want you to get some good, usable footage...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.28,0:49:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可用的錄像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of his killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.71,0:49:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后銷毀其他一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then destroy everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.61,0:49:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要發布約書亞·馬斯特森被殺的視頻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will be releasing footage of Joshua Masterson's killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.21,0:49:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府和情報機構\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The administration and the intelligence community
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.22,0:49:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本希望活捉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were hoping to take him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.25,0:49:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想贊揚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would like to commend
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.20,0:49:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反恐處助理局長  納森·格林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assistant Director of Counterterrorism, Nathan Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.23,0:49:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然還有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And of course all of the work
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.22,0:49:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國務卿杜蘭特做的一切相關幕后工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Secretary Durant has done behind the scenes on all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.12,0:49:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查目前為止收集到的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The information the investigation has gathered so far
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.58,0:49:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表明約書亞·馬斯特森和扎克瑞·霍桑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}points to Joshua Masterson and Zachary Hawthorne
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.42,0:49:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟海外的哈里發國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}having strong connections to ICO abroad
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.98,0:49:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和國內在發展的哈里發國網絡有密切關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and ICO's growing network domestically.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.84,0:50:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想直接對哈里發國說以下這些話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so I would like to say this to ICO directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.38,0:50:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們再別想左右哪怕一個年輕人的頭腦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will not infect the mind of one more of our young people,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.36,0:50:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不會罷休  直到我找到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I will not stop until I find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.75,0:50:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話也說給悲痛中的米勒一家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I say that for the grieving Miller family,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.87,0:50:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他們今晚能睡得著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whom I hope will find some sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.49,0:50:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還敦促國會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also urge Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.51,0:50:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加快進程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to accelerate the process
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.97,0:50:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我的宣戰請求做出表決\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and vote on my request for a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.40,0:50:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統先生  -我不會回答問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. President? - I will not be answering questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.78,0:50:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來賽斯會接手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth will take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.57,0:50:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好分辨  但那應該是致命一擊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard to see, but I think that was the killshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.93,0:50:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請記住  這些報道尚未經證實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, please remember, these reports are unconfirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.58,0:50:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還在等待白宮的聲明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we're waiting on a statement from the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.20,0:50:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以報道  有大量...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we can report is a great deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.21,0:50:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you watching this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.68,0:50:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...這片林區  有槍擊聲  既有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...this wooded area. And shots being fired, both by and--
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.58,0:50:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.83,0:50:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我是弗蘭西斯·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello. This is Francis Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.06,0:50:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.73,0:51:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委員會在找雷米·丹頓和杰姬·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The committee is looking for Remy Danton and Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.09,0:51:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們跟哈里發國和戰爭有什么關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do either of them have to do with ICO or the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.00,0:51:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國會那邊的消息是他們會要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The talk up on the Hill is they're going to invite you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.16,0:51:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的手下去作證\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the rest of your staff to testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.71,0:51:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們要利用宣戰的事做調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're gonna use the Declaration of War to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.81,0:51:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.22,0:51:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們要用弗蘭克要求組建的委員會調查他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're gonna use the committee Frank asked for to investigate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.25,0:51:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-該死  -是啊  道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fuck. - That's right, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.45,0:51:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"該死"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Fuck."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.28,0:51:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難理解...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's difficult to underst--
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.84,0:51:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許如果你能稍稍平靜一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, perhaps if you could just calm down for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.60,0:51:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.64,0:51:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為這消息能給你帶來一絲寬慰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought this news would bring you some relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.30,0:51:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統打給了米勒太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president called Mrs. Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.49,0:51:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你和你女兒保證過  我會...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promised you and your daughter that I would--
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.53,0:51:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放過她吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.76,0:51:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我們還是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, perhaps we should speak
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.14,0:51:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你好一些了再談吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you're feeling a little more up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.52,0:51:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想聽到你說話  或收到你的任何消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to hear you. Or from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.71,0:51:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你對我們家做的事...  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What you did to my family... - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.42,0:51:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我們扯進去  別用我丈夫的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave us out of it. And do not use my husband's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.53,0:51:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, Mrs.--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.11,0:52:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她掛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.00,0:52:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去走走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.48,0:52:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.86,0:52:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出他們想聽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell them what they need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.59,0:52:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.48,0:52:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.56,0:52:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  謝謝  謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President. Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.98,0:53:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.45,0:53:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們完全不需要害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.03,0:53:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們完全不需要害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.36,0:53:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全不需要害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have nothing to be afraid of.
